div.div: A special, multi-part side story manga set in the world of Mairimashita! Iruma-kun, focusing on Kalego during his days as a student of Babyls Demon School.
Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo!

Kazuma Sato is a video game-loving shut-in-or at least he was, until a humiliating traffic accident brings his young life to an untimely end. But after his death, a beautiful girl claiming to be a goddess invites him to enter another world and gain some respectable perks in the process. But Kazuma's choice is going to have serious consequences for the goddess and the dead man alike... (Source: Yen Press)
Otonari no Tenshi-sama ni Itsunomanika Dame Ningen ni Sareteita Ken

Amane Fujimiya lives alone in a messy apartment—right next door to Mahiru Shiina, a veritable "angel" who's the smartest, prettiest girl at school. When a chance encounter on a rainy day draws them together, Mahiru finds herself spending more and more time helping Amane get his life in order. And though they both insist they have no intention of dating the other, slowly but surely, something more than friendship begins to blossom.
(Source: Square Enix)
Tokidoki Bosotto Russiago de Dereru Tonari no Alya-san

Masachika Kuse sits next to Alya, a girl of Russian and Japanese descent. She's beautiful, haughty, and an exceptional student, while Masachika is nerdy and known for being a slacker. He's an easy target for her comments in Russian, which she's all too happy to translateexcept he can understand what she's really saying!
(Source: K Manga)
